&lt;li&gt;Experience in the Electrical, Heating, and/or HVAC field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must also have knowledge and understanding of computers and circuits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must have a clean and valid driver&#39;s license&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Located in the Boston Metro area&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
