&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effective multi-tasking and efficient time management capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Natural initiative and problem solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong sense of ownership in work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Positive attitude&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Computer literacy with experience in Microsoft Office and Google Docs/Sheets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conversational Spanish is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
